    public enum MusicPlayer
extends java.lang.Enum<MusicPlayer>

    MusicPlayer

    The MusicPlayer class is an singleton class of utility to provide some methods to play sounds in different pages

    Note: this class is implemented as an Enum thus to be a singleton class.

    Main Functionality: 

                    MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.playStartScreenMusic();
                MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.playSelectMusic();
                MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.playGameMusic();
                MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.playLoseMusic();
                MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.playWinMusic();

    Use: 

                    MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.init();
                MusicPlayer.INSTANCE.{PLAY_MUSIC_METHOD}();
    从以下版本开始:
    1.0
    版本:
    1.0
    作者:
    Wenzheng Shan
